    "description": {
      "zh": "7.92x57毫米全金属被甲弹（FMJ）是一款内裹8g铅芯的198格令比赛级弹头，可穿透NIJ III级防弹护甲；由Rifle Line弹药公司生产，适用于狩猎、家庭防卫及靶场训练。尽管不在主流口径内，这款弹药仍能对目标造成显著伤害。",
      "en": "7.92x57mm Full Metal Jacket (FMJ) is a 198 grain match round with an 8 gram lead core designed to penetrate up to NIJ Level III armor; Intended for hunting, home defense, and target practice, produced by Rifle Line Ammunition. Despite not being a commonly adopted caliber, this cartridge is capable of outputting oustanding damage to its targets."
    },
